ver.com/read?oid=076&aid=0003370160|title=\ub354\ubcf4\uc774\uc988, \ub370\ubdd4 \uccab \u4e9e\ud22c\uc5b4 \ud655\uc815\u2026\ud32c\ucf58 '\ub354 \uce90\uc2ac' 8\uac1c\uad6d \uac1c\ucd5c |access-date=January 18, 2019|language=ko}}</ref> The group released their second single album ''Bloom Bloom'' and its lead single \"Bloom Bloom\" on April 29, 2019.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.osen.co.kr/article/G1111132103|title=\ub354\ubcf4\uc774\uc988, \uc624\ub298(29\uc77c) \uc2e0\uace1 '\ube14\ub8f8\ube14\ub8f8'\uc73c\ub85c \ucef4\ubc31..V\ub77c\uc774\ube0c \uc0dd\uc911\uacc4[\uacf5\uc2dd] |work=osen|language=ko|accessdate=April 29, 2019}}</ref> On 7 May, Kevin received his first-ever [[Music programs of South Korea#Chart Systems|music show win]] on [[SBS MTV]]'s ''[[The Show (South Korean TV series)|The Show]]'' with The Boyz.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://entertain.naver.com/read?oid=311&aid=0000988059|title='\ub354\uc1fc' \ub354\ubcf4\uc774\uc988, \uc5d4\ud50c\ub77c\uc789\u00b7\ubc15\ubd04 \uc81c\uce58\uace0 1\uc704 \ucc28\uc9c0 [\uc885\ud569] |work=Naver|language=ko|accessdate=May 7, 2019}}</ref>\n\n== Discography ==\n{{main|The Boyz (South Korean band)#Discography}}\n\n=== Soundtrack appearances ===\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-align:center;\"\n! scope=\"col\" |Year\n! scope=\"col\" |Title\n! scope=\"col\" |Album\n|-\n|2017\n! scope=\"row\" |\"Half\"\n| ''[[Saimdang, Light's Diary]]'' OST\n|}\n\n== References ==\n<!--- See http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wikipedia:Footnotes on how to create references using <ref></ref> tags, these references will then appear here automatically -->\n{{Reflist}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Moon, Kevin}}\n<!--- Categories --->\n[[Category:Korean-language singers of Canada]]\n[[Category:1998 births]]\n[[Category:Canadian musicians of Korean descent]]\n[[Category:South Korean television personalities]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n", "name_user": "89.23.224.59", "label": "unsafe", "comment": "", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ke